  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/a153f440cdd4a61396ae6ec0c1410da3.avif?t=1695136290\" width=614 height=200 /></span><br><br>In the game 《League TD》, there are many distinctive defense towers that can be obtained through continuous battles. Having enough materials can unlock higher level defense towers. Each type of defense tower can be continuously upgraded to enhance its attack ability, while unlocking different performance accessories, allowing the defense tower to have different attack skills. A reasonable selection of defense towers with various functional accessories can give your defense front more possibilities.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/02fd2487c435e68b6cd01fda42085c20.avif?t=1695136290\" width=614 height=168 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TOWER</h2><br>Rich and colorful defense towers, each with its own unique attack method.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/a1a5d4a82f9ae34d97bd03ed8da365d0.poster.avif?t=1695136290\" width=500 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/a1a5d4a82f9ae34d97bd03ed8da365d0.webm?t=1695136290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/a1a5d4a82f9ae34d97bd03ed8da365d0.mp4?t=1695136290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/0f7453219a418c84149c7e20b58c0173.poster.avif?t=1695136290\" width=500 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/0f7453219a418c84149c7e20b58c0173.webm?t=1695136290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/0f7453219a418c84149c7e20b58c0173.mp4?t=1695136290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/dae7c5087f1843197b46e77c88297b44.poster.avif?t=1695136290\" width=500 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/dae7c5087f1843197b46e77c88297b44.webm?t=1695136290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/dae7c5087f1843197b46e77c88297b44.mp4?t=1695136290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade Defense Tower</h2><br>Each type of defense tower can be upgraded to level 10, and its performance will improve with the upgrade.<br>The upgraded defense tower can achieve higher attack power, speed of fire, and longer range.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/208576d5b010b3a5e6ad63fe7a58ecf5.poster.avif?t=1695136290\" width=268 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/208576d5b010b3a5e6ad63fe7a58ecf5.webm?t=1695136290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/208576d5b010b3a5e6ad63fe7a58ecf5.mp4?t=1695136290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/c6310fa2cb9c383394221edd1a078a07.poster.avif?t=1695136290\" width=268 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/c6310fa2cb9c383394221edd1a078a07.webm?t=1695136290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/c6310fa2cb9c383394221edd1a078a07.mp4?t=1695136290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defense Tower Accessories</h2><br>As the level of the defense tower increases, 10 different functional accessories can be unlocked.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/a2caba82cf44f6502d8a345a972b1922.poster.avif?t=1695136290\" width=398 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/a2caba82cf44f6502d8a345a972b1922.webm?t=1695136290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/a2caba82cf44f6502d8a345a972b1922.mp4?t=1695136290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/9502ee732f1d23e6ebf505d1f09b0459.poster.avif?t=1695136290\" width=398 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/9502ee732f1d23e6ebf505d1f09b0459.webm?t=1695136290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/9502ee732f1d23e6ebf505d1f09b0459.mp4?t=1695136290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defense Tower Skills</h2><br>Upgrading different defense tower accessories can result in different skills or performance improvements. There are many types of skills for defense towers, which can be used to build a variety of combinations.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/1b762fdd978a0e79794f3c980e71ef83.poster.avif?t=1695136290\" width=400 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/1b762fdd978a0e79794f3c980e71ef83.webm?t=1695136290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/1b762fdd978a0e79794f3c980e71ef83.mp4?t=1695136290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >enemy</h2><br>Rich variety of enemies.<br>Most enemies have their own means of defense or counterattack.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/cd0fb7c73a2f88f4c862753dbcd83510.poster.avif?t=1695136290\" width=400 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/cd0fb7c73a2f88f4c862753dbcd83510.webm?t=1695136290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535970/extras/cd0fb7c73a2f88f4c862753dbcd83510.mp4?t=1695136290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Are you ready? The enemy won't obediently surrender, let's start fighting together.",
